Tā gēnběn méi yìshi dào zìjǐ de xíngwéi yǒu duōme zìsī.
Yǒu le qián, nǐ jiù yǒu xuǎnzé de zìyóu.
Wèile wánchéng zhège xiàngmù, yuángōng men dōu zìyuàn liú xiàlai jiābān.
Xìngmíng de shǒuzìmǔ yào dàxiě.
Wǒmen zài shìpín zhōng jiāshàng le Zhōng Yīng shuāngyǔ zìmù.
Guānyú shìfǒu tóuzī zhège xiàngmù, wǒmen huì zōnghé suǒyǒu gǔdōng de yìjiàn zài zuò juédìng.
